Compilation flags:
========================================
Enable : MODEL=HYDRO, MHD
Disable: GRAVITY, PARTICLE


Default setup:
========================================
1. Periodic BC
2. Refinement criterion: current density (OPT__FLAG_CURRENT)
3. MAX_LEVEL = 2


Note:
========================================
1. Reference: Orszag & Tang, 1998, J. Fluid Mech., 90, 129
2. No z dependence
